    <details class="fq"><summary>Other nutrients that help collagen?</summary><p>Copper, zinc, silica, vitamin A, glycine, and proline all support collagen synthesis.</p></details>
    <details class="fq"><summary>Enough C from a collagen gummy alone?</summary><p>If it has 60-90mg, yes. If less, pair with dietary sources or a vitamin C gummy.</p></details>
    <details class="fq"><summary>Does C + collagen prevent sun damage?</summary><p>Partially — C neutralizes UV free radicals. Combine with topical C and SPF for best protection.</p></details>

